                <p>Have you heard the linnet trilling,</p>
                <p> To discover did you try</p>
                <p>What is hidden in her carolâ€”</p>
                <p> Does she sing or does she cry?</p>
                <p/>
                <p>I am singing like the linnet,</p>
                <p> When my heart does pine and long;</p>
                <p>Love, and pain, and joy, and sorrow,</p>
                <p> All are hidden in my song.</p>
